00:14:33,040 --> 00:14:34,340
and I was stunned.

247
00:14:35,200 --> 00:14:36,260
I never expected

248
00:14:36,300 --> 00:14:39,120
our school to have
such a legit cheerleading squad.

249
00:14:39,620 --> 00:14:40,740
You didn't even look like you.

250
00:14:41,240 --> 00:14:43,660
But at the same time,
you were like a whole new you.

251
00:14:46,740 --> 00:14:48,100
Is this "new me"

252
00:14:48,600 --> 00:14:50,960
because of what I was wearing that day?

253
00:14:51,720 --> 00:14:52,560
No.

254
00:14:54,580 --> 00:14:57,300
Back when we were
in middle school at Qunshan,

255
00:14:57,340 --> 00:14:59,660
for all three years, you barely spoke.

256
00:14:59,700 --> 00:15:01,900
You hardly ever
joined in class activities.

257
00:15:02,400 --> 00:15:04,240
You left right after school.

258
00:15:04,280 --> 00:15:06,500
Back then,
I thought you were just introverted,

259
00:15:07,560 --> 00:15:08,640
always…

260
00:15:08,680 --> 00:15:10,220
quiet and expressionless,

261
00:15:10,260 --> 00:15:11,740
like Lu Xueqi.

262
00:15:12,780 --> 00:15:14,660
Have you been writing too many novels?

263
00:15:14,700 --> 00:15:16,640
You're starting to
see everyone as a character.

264
00:15:18,540 --> 00:15:19,520
But later

265
00:15:20,160 --> 00:15:21,380
I realized I was wrong.

266
00:15:21,420 --> 00:15:23,760
That wasn't the real you.

267
00:15:23,800 --> 00:15:26,160
The you at Experimental High
is the true you,

268
00:15:26,660 --> 00:15:29,840
or the one at Qunshan Middle School
was a new you.

269
00:15:42,920 --> 00:15:44,860
It doesn't feel much different

270
00:15:45,460 --> 00:15:47,000
from a regular classroom.

271
00:15:48,640 --> 00:15:50,820
Whether it's me, Jiang Qiaoxi,

272
00:15:51,320 --> 00:15:53,300
or anyone in this advanced class,

273
00:15:53,800 --> 00:15:55,780
we're no different from regular humans.

274
00:15:55,820 --> 00:15:57,080
Just carbon-based lifeforms.

275
00:15:59,840 --> 00:16:00,960
This was my seat.

276
00:16:05,680 --> 00:16:07,620
Didn't you finish packing already?

277
00:16:09,760 --> 00:16:10,860
Been done for a while.

278
00:16:19,140 --> 00:16:20,020
Lin Qile.

279
00:16:21,220 --> 00:16:22,060
What is it?

280
00:16:22,560 --> 00:16:23,980
Do you think I'm qualified?

281
00:16:26,560 --> 00:16:29,500
Qualified for what?

282
00:16:29,540 --> 00:16:31,620
Now that the college entrance exams
are over.

283
00:16:32,300 --> 00:16:33,580
We're almost university students.

284
00:16:33,620 --> 00:16:35,440
Throughout that final countdown,

285
00:16:35,940 --> 00:16:37,920
I've been keeping
another timer in my heart.

286
00:16:38,780 --> 00:16:39,620
I waited all this time

287
00:16:40,120 --> 00:16:42,620
because I wanted to tell you now,
at this very moment.

288
00:16:43,160 --> 00:16:45,960
I hope to be in a deeper relationship
with you, more than being classmates.

289
00:16:47,140 --> 00:16:48,060
Will you?

290
00:17:11,339 --> 00:17:12,200
Monitor.

291
00:17:13,940 --> 00:17:14,780
I'm sorry.

292
00:17:15,319 --> 00:17:16,520
Lin Qile,

293
00:17:17,440 --> 00:17:18,940
you've done nothing wrong.

294
00:17:19,540 --> 00:17:20,780
The fault is entirely mine.

295
00:17:21,640 --> 00:17:23,220
I knew your answer.

296
00:17:23,780 --> 00:17:25,099
Yet I asked anyway,

297
00:17:25,640 --> 00:17:26,720
forcing this burden upon you.

298
00:17:29,020 --> 00:17:30,040
But…

299
00:17:30,080 --> 00:17:31,400
you didn't come here today

300
00:17:32,580 --> 00:17:34,000
just to help me pack, did you?

301
00:17:35,900 --> 00:17:36,960
You know it.

302
00:17:37,720 --> 00:17:39,120
I knew it.

303
00:17:39,160 --> 00:17:40,700
You came to see

304
00:17:41,560 --> 00:17:43,480
Jiang Qiaoxi's seat, didn't you?

305
00:17:49,100 --> 00:17:50,380
Right over there.

306
00:18:04,160 --> 00:18:05,440
I always thought

307
00:18:06,960 --> 00:18:08,400
he'd come back

308
00:18:08,940 --> 00:18:10,600
for these things after May.

309
00:18:13,040 --> 00:18:14,320
Take his things back for him.

310
00:18:42,220 --> 00:18:43,460
I get it.

311
00:18:43,500 --> 00:18:44,420
Jiang Qiaoxi,

312
00:18:44,920 --> 00:18:47,360
a genius, a star who were born lucky.

313
00:18:48,500 --> 00:18:49,700
What do I have to compete?

314
00:18:49,740 --> 00:18:51,300
What could I ever win?

315
00:18:53,440 --> 00:18:54,660
He's no lucky star.

316
00:18:58,540 --> 00:18:59,820
He fought bitterly for it.

317
00:19:01,280 --> 00:19:03,000
Every step of the way.

318
00:19:14,920 --> 00:19:16,200
HALL OF KNOWLEDGE AND ACTION

319
00:19:16,240 --> 00:19:17,120
Is it heavy?

320
00:19:17,160 --> 00:19:18,440
Do you need me to carry it for you?

321
00:19:18,480 --> 00:19:19,840
No. I can do it myself.

322
00:19:20,380 --> 00:19:22,540
Yingtao, you don't need to worry so much.

323
00:19:22,580 --> 00:19:23,880
He'll definitely come back.

324
00:19:24,960 --> 00:19:27,480
A junior named Qi Le once told me

325
00:19:27,520 --> 00:19:29,020
how exhausting those Olympiads were,

326
00:19:29,060 --> 00:19:30,020
back-to-back exams.

327
00:19:30,060 --> 00:19:31,160
Some would leave the venue

328
00:19:31,200 --> 00:19:32,960
and wander outside till midnight.

329
00:19:33,000 --> 00:19:34,400
Others refuse to return,

330
00:19:34,440 --> 00:19:36,120
heading straight to
tourist spots to unwind.

331
00:19:36,620 --> 00:19:37,880
But not Jiang Qiaoxi.

332
00:19:37,920 --> 00:19:39,260
He'd only call you,

333
00:19:39,800 --> 00:19:40,640
rain or shine.

334
00:19:41,140 --> 00:19:42,940
After every exam, every single day,

335
00:19:42,980 --> 00:19:44,220
he'd call you,

336
00:19:44,820 --> 00:19:46,280
never mind who might see.

337
00:19:46,320 --> 00:19:48,540
That demeanor of his, how to describe it?

338
00:19:49,580 --> 00:19:50,680
Unrestrained.

339
00:19:50,720 --> 00:19:51,680
Recklessly bold.

340
00:19:54,540 --> 00:19:56,320
So don't you worry.

341
00:19:56,820 --> 00:19:58,280
Yes, he had to leave for school,

342
00:19:59,700 --> 00:20:01,320
but I guarantee

343
00:20:01,980 --> 00:20:03,180
the moment he returns,

344
00:20:03,720 --> 00:20:04,960
you'll be his first to find.

345
00:20:26,540 --> 00:20:28,600
BUILDING A BETTER POWER COMMUNITY TOGETHER

346
00:21:24,220 --> 00:21:25,200
I promise you

347
00:21:26,700 --> 00:21:27,820
and Chunlu too.

348
00:21:29,500 --> 00:21:30,840
I'll come home soon

349
00:22:02,200 --> 00:22:03,280
Jiang Qiaoxi?

350
00:22:26,760 --> 00:22:28,380
Are you stealing from your own family?

351
00:22:36,900 --> 00:22:37,740
Yingtao,

352
00:22:38,500 --> 00:22:39,440
what are you saying?

353
00:22:39,980 --> 00:22:41,340
Why are you sneaking around

354
00:22:43,060 --> 00:22:44,320
your own home like a thief?

355
00:22:48,100 --> 00:22:49,900
Are you running away again?

356
00:23:01,720 --> 00:23:02,760
What do you think,

357
00:23:04,580 --> 00:23:05,600
Yingtao?

358
00:23:06,260 --> 00:23:07,260
I think…

359
00:23:13,180 --> 00:23:14,140
I think…

360
00:23:17,900 --> 00:23:19,180
you're here to see me.

361
00:23:34,700 --> 00:23:35,580
Right.

362
00:23:36,260 --> 00:23:37,440
I'm not going abroad.

363
00:23:38,820 --> 00:23:39,880
I want to…

364
00:23:41,140 --> 00:23:42,140
stay right here,

365
00:23:42,720 --> 00:23:43,920
with you.

366
00:23:46,660 --> 00:23:48,000
You're not going abroad?

367
00:23:51,300 --> 00:23:52,680
I knew it.

368
00:23:52,720 --> 00:23:55,580
You wouldn't just
cut me off for no reason.

369
00:23:55,620 --> 00:23:57,460
You wouldn't vanish without cause.

370
00:23:58,000 --> 00:23:59,400
They must have cut your phone line,

371
00:23:59,440 --> 00:24:01,820
and my letters,
torn to pieces again, right?

372
00:24:04,320 --> 00:24:05,340
Jiang Qiaoxi.

373
00:24:06,720 --> 00:24:08,240
You'd never leave me willingly.

374
00:24:08,740 --> 00:24:09,580
Tell me I'm right.

375
00:24:15,120 --> 00:24:16,200
Of course.

376
00:24:18,540 --> 00:24:20,520
I've been well in Hong Kong.

377
00:24:21,480 --> 00:24:22,540
My cousin too.

378
00:24:23,040 --> 00:24:24,340
He even has a daughter now.

379
00:24:25,940 --> 00:24:27,740
I am also studying well

380
00:24:29,300 --> 00:24:30,360
in Hong Kong.

381
00:24:30,960 --> 00:24:31,980
You know how it is.

382
00:24:32,560 --> 00:24:34,920
Top marks, as always.

383
00:24:36,020 --> 00:24:37,620
Could've picked any university.

384
00:24:39,960 --> 00:24:40,860
But…

385
00:24:41,440 --> 00:24:42,740
I don't want any of that.

386
00:24:43,240 --> 00:24:44,780
Because none of those places

387
00:24:47,040 --> 00:24:48,480
have you, Lin Yingtao.

388
00:24:50,980 --> 00:24:52,600
Or Auntie's jujube buns.

389
00:24:55,620 --> 00:24:56,460
So I…

390
00:25:00,760 --> 00:25:01,780
I think I'll stay.

391
00:25:07,260 --> 00:25:10,060
Good that you are not going now.

392
00:25:10,580 --> 00:25:12,140
Having you by my side is everything.

393
00:25:12,640 --> 00:25:16,040
Haven't I always taken you
to the best places?

394
00:25:18,160 --> 00:25:19,160
And did you

395
00:25:19,720 --> 00:25:20,800
read my texts?

396
00:25:21,340 --> 00:25:23,500
Do you know how well I did
on the college entrance exam?

397
00:25:24,660 --> 00:25:25,560
I know.

398
00:25:27,700 --> 00:25:28,900
Northern Normal University, right?

399
00:25:30,140 --> 00:25:31,780
Never imagined you'd score that well.

400
00:25:33,120 --> 00:25:33,960
Well…

401
00:25:35,060 --> 00:25:36,640
with your Olympiad results,

402
00:25:37,140 --> 00:25:40,160
you could've waltzed into
any top university in Hongyang.

403
00:25:40,720 --> 00:25:41,720
And you know

404
00:25:41,760 --> 00:25:44,980
all the best ones are just a stone's throw
from Northern Normal University.

405
00:25:46,840 --> 00:25:47,780
I know.

406
00:25:48,580 --> 00:25:49,620
And I…

407
00:25:50,840 --> 00:25:54,220
I'll pick the campus closest to yours.

408
00:25:55,560 --> 00:25:56,780
That way,

409
00:25:56,820 --> 00:25:58,660
we can walk to class together…

410
00:26:00,840 --> 00:26:02,180
queue at the same canteen,

411
00:26:03,360 --> 00:26:05,520
and just…

412
00:26:06,160 --> 00:26:07,460
be together.

413
00:26:11,320 --> 00:26:12,420
What you said…

414
00:26:14,700 --> 00:26:15,680
Is it real?

415
00:26:16,500 --> 00:26:17,760
We could really be…

416
00:26:18,780 --> 00:26:20,480
together every day?

417
00:26:21,840 --> 00:26:24,320
Of course. When have I ever lied to you?

418
00:26:28,320 --> 00:26:29,160
You're right.

419
00:26:31,460 --> 00:26:32,660
You've always achieved everything

420
00:26:33,160 --> 00:26:34,000
you set your mind to.

421
00:26:39,940 --> 00:26:41,400
But…

422
00:26:42,880 --> 00:26:44,700
when you said it, why do you sound like

423
00:26:45,240 --> 00:26:46,600
you're holding back tears?

424
00:26:50,260 --> 00:26:51,240
No.

425
00:26:52,240 --> 00:26:53,300
It's just…

426
00:26:54,180 --> 00:26:55,320
it's just that…

427
00:26:57,900 --> 00:26:59,100
when I imagine

428
00:26:59,880 --> 00:27:01,460
our future together so bright,

429
00:27:02,740 --> 00:27:04,080
this happiness feels unbearable.

430
00:27:11,340 --> 00:27:12,840
Then I want proof.

431
00:27:14,800 --> 00:27:16,020
What proof?

432
00:27:42,060 --> 00:27:43,280
Do you have little fang teeth?

433
00:28:56,980 --> 00:28:57,820
Yingtao.

434
00:29:03,600 --> 00:29:04,700
Don't forget me.

435
00:29:22,020 --> 00:29:22,860
Yingtao.

436
00:29:24,020 --> 00:29:25,300
I want to eat

437
00:29:26,260 --> 00:29:27,660
jujube buns made by Auntie.

438
00:29:28,300 --> 00:29:29,840
You're so lucky.

439
00:29:30,340 --> 00:29:31,560
My mom made

440
00:29:32,060 --> 00:29:33,360
a lot today.

441
00:29:35,540 --> 00:29:37,580
Then let's go back to eat.

442
00:29:38,380 --> 00:29:39,220
Okay.

443
00:29:40,140 --> 00:29:40,980
Let's go.

444
00:29:57,700 --> 00:29:58,660
Jiang Qiaoxi.

445
00:29:59,020 --> 00:29:59,860
‪Yes?

446
00:30:02,420 --> 00:30:03,460
Jiang Qiaoxi.

447
00:30:09,980 --> 00:30:12,800
Jiang Qiaoxi.

448
00:30:19,480 --> 00:30:20,320
Jiang Qiaoxi.

449
00:30:22,380 --> 00:30:23,720
When our future arrives…

450
00:30:24,240 --> 00:30:27,360
when we're truly together every day,

451
00:30:28,340 --> 00:30:30,460
could you wear…

452
00:30:30,960 --> 00:30:31,980
brighter colors?

453
00:30:32,020 --> 00:30:34,580
No more of these muted grays. Please?

454
00:30:35,440 --> 00:30:38,640
Every time you dress in sunlight hues,

455
00:30:38,680 --> 00:30:41,180
it's like watching joy made visible.

456
00:30:42,020 --> 00:30:43,340
I think you feel it too.

457
00:30:44,520 --> 00:30:46,300
I don't look good in brighter colors.

458
00:30:46,800 --> 00:30:48,360
Good-looking.

459
00:30:48,400 --> 00:30:49,340
Good-looking!

460
00:30:51,100 --> 00:30:53,020
Okay, I'll wear it later.

461
00:31:02,700 --> 00:31:04,900
Jiang Qiaoxi.

462
00:31:05,720 --> 00:31:07,640
Jiang Qiaoxi.

463
00:31:08,560 --> 00:31:10,420
Jiang Qiaoxi.

464
00:31:17,200 --> 00:31:18,040
- Yingtao.
- Hm?

465
00:31:21,640 --> 00:31:23,960
Don't you think I'm missing something?

466
00:31:29,660 --> 00:31:30,640
What's missing?

467
00:31:32,680 --> 00:31:33,840
My suitcase.

468
00:31:37,480 --> 00:31:38,320
Right.

469
00:31:38,960 --> 00:31:41,440
Where is the suitcase?

470
00:31:43,680 --> 00:31:45,020
It's probably at my doorstep.

471
00:31:45,660 --> 00:31:48,400
Hope no one's taken it.

472
00:31:56,180 --> 00:31:57,820
Look, here's the plan:

473
00:31:57,860 --> 00:31:59,740
you go up first
and start steaming the buns.

474
00:31:59,780 --> 00:32:01,100
I'll dash back for the suitcase.

475
00:32:01,140 --> 00:32:02,840
I'll be back just as they're ready to eat.

476
00:32:07,820 --> 00:32:08,960
Okay.

477
00:32:10,060 --> 00:32:10,900
Go.

478
00:32:18,000 --> 00:32:19,000
Jiang Qiaoxi.

479
00:32:19,620 --> 00:32:22,180
When we see my parents upstairs,

480
00:32:22,840 --> 00:32:24,340
you tell them…

481
00:32:25,660 --> 00:32:26,720
we met on the way here.

482
00:32:27,460 --> 00:32:29,500
And I'm warning you,
not a single word out of line.

483
00:32:30,480 --> 00:32:32,380
Sure. I won't.

484
00:32:44,640 --> 00:32:45,640
Jiang Qiaoxi.

485
00:32:52,120 --> 00:32:53,200
What is it?

486
00:32:55,720 --> 00:32:56,980
I like you.

487
00:32:59,340 --> 00:33:00,900
I like you very much.

488
00:33:09,400 --> 00:33:10,520
I know.

489
00:33:18,640 --> 00:33:19,480
I love you.

490
00:33:35,400 --> 00:33:36,620
Go back.

491
00:34:01,100 --> 00:34:02,040
<i>Who's there?</i>

492
00:34:02,720 --> 00:34:03,580
<i>Who's there?</i>

493
00:34:04,560 --> 00:34:05,760
<i>Me.</i>

494
00:34:06,260 --> 00:34:08,000
<i>Didn't you bring the key?</i>

495
00:34:08,040 --> 00:34:09,199
I forgot.

496
00:34:12,400 --> 00:34:13,340
What are you doing?

497
00:34:13,380 --> 00:34:15,400
I'll warm up the jujube buns.

498
00:34:15,440 --> 00:34:16,800
Jiang Qiaoxi's hungry. He's craving them.

499
00:34:17,800 --> 00:34:18,960
- Qiaoxi?
- Yes.

500
00:34:20,100 --> 00:34:21,260
Qiaoxi's back?

501
00:34:22,780 --> 00:34:24,060
I…

502
00:34:24,100 --> 00:34:27,760
I was passing his place
when I just happened to see

503
00:34:28,260 --> 00:34:29,460
him step out.

504
00:34:29,500 --> 00:34:31,500
He's gone back to grab his luggage now.

505
00:34:32,000 --> 00:34:33,179
He'll be right over.

506
00:34:35,500 --> 00:34:37,679
That's not how you steam buns.
Here, let me.

507
00:34:39,100 --> 00:34:40,340
Just go wait over there.

508
00:34:52,760 --> 00:34:53,679
What are you doing?

509
00:34:53,719 --> 00:34:55,280
- Stuffed lotus roots.
- Don't turn it on.

510
00:34:56,219 --> 00:34:57,160
Later,

511
00:34:57,700 --> 00:34:59,640
Mom will fry them properly in the pan.

512
00:35:04,180 --> 00:35:05,340
Stop pouring like that.

513
00:35:05,380 --> 00:35:07,400
Just leave it. I'll handle it.

514
00:35:08,040 --> 00:35:08,880
Fine.

515
00:35:32,040 --> 00:35:33,240
<i>What are you doing, Yingtao?</i>

516
00:35:34,700 --> 00:35:35,580
I…

517
00:35:36,080 --> 00:35:37,760
I was wondering why he hadn't come yet.

518
00:35:38,260 --> 00:35:39,100
<i>Who?</i>

519
00:35:40,360 --> 00:35:41,200
Jiang Qiaoxi.

520
00:36:06,800 --> 00:36:07,740
<i>Hello.</i>

521
00:36:07,780 --> 00:36:10,980
<i>The subscriber you have dialed</i>
<i>is currently unavailable.</i>

522
00:36:11,020 --> 00:36:12,460
<i>Please try your call again later.</i>

523
00:36:25,760 --> 00:36:26,680
<i>Hello.</i>

524
00:36:26,720 --> 00:36:29,820
<i>The subscriber you have dialed</i>
<i>is currently unavailable.</i>

525
00:36:29,860 --> 00:36:31,340
<i>Please try your call again later.</i>

526
00:36:37,740 --> 00:36:38,580
<i>Where are you going?</i>

527
00:36:38,620 --> 00:36:39,900
<i>You just got back. Heading out again?</i>

528
00:36:39,940 --> 00:36:40,920
Yingtao!

