565
00:40:47,700 --> 00:40:49,720
<i>like a sudden tsunami.</i>

566
00:40:49,760 --> 00:40:51,180
<i>A devastating blow to the world economy…</i>

567
00:40:51,220 --> 00:40:53,480
They say it is the most
severe economic crisis

568
00:40:53,520 --> 00:40:55,500
since the Great Depression of 1929.

569
00:40:55,540 --> 00:40:57,600
And now, just as our child starts college,

570
00:40:57,640 --> 00:40:58,980
at the beginning of their adult life,

571
00:40:59,020 --> 00:41:01,020
they have to face
such tremendous upheaval.

572
00:41:02,880 --> 00:41:05,080
<i>A generation's fate and challenges.</i>

573
00:41:05,120 --> 00:41:06,800
<i>Let the kids forge their own path.</i>

574
00:41:07,500 --> 00:41:09,320
<i>What is with this year?</i>

575
00:41:09,820 --> 00:41:12,520
<i>Natural disasters, economic crises.</i>

576
00:41:13,020 --> 00:41:14,620
<i>Everyone's tightening their belts.</i>

577
00:41:15,220 --> 00:41:17,660
Even my mart's feeling the pinch.

578
00:41:18,220 --> 00:41:19,240
Don't worry, Qin.

579
00:41:19,780 --> 00:41:20,860
The country is boosting domestic demands.

580
00:41:21,360 --> 00:41:23,000
Haven't you heard?
They are adjusting the interest rates.

581
00:41:23,040 --> 00:41:24,340
Once investments start flowing in,

582
00:41:24,380 --> 00:41:26,960
- the economy will bounce back in no time.
- Exactly!

583
00:41:28,880 --> 00:41:29,860
Great!

584
00:41:31,860 --> 00:41:33,620
This carp shape is spot-on!

585
00:41:33,660 --> 00:41:36,100
You've really captured that energy
of triumphant leap to success

586
00:41:37,500 --> 00:41:38,900
I've learnt this dish ages ago.

587
00:41:38,940 --> 00:41:42,040
I am saving it for today,
for when the kids got into college.

588
00:41:42,080 --> 00:41:42,960
Now, let me show you.

589
00:41:43,460 --> 00:41:44,600
Amazing you!

590
00:41:45,140 --> 00:41:47,420
I still see them as little kids,

591
00:41:47,460 --> 00:41:49,180
and now poof,
they're already college students.

592
00:41:50,140 --> 00:41:52,820
When Yingtao was little,
she hated studying,

593
00:41:52,860 --> 00:41:54,440
always off playing somewhere.

594
00:41:54,480 --> 00:41:55,980
Back then, I was thinking,

595
00:41:56,020 --> 00:41:58,800
will this kid even make it to college?

596
00:41:58,840 --> 00:42:00,680
No need to worry now.

597
00:42:00,720 --> 00:42:03,840
Yingtao scored the highest
of all the kids.

598
00:42:03,880 --> 00:42:05,900
Even a solid dozen points
above our Yu Qiao.

599
00:42:07,520 --> 00:42:08,360
And Du Shang,

600
00:42:08,400 --> 00:42:10,140
remember that tiny kid

601
00:42:10,180 --> 00:42:11,680
always practicing martial arts?

602
00:42:12,180 --> 00:42:13,960
Now he's gotten into medical school.

603
00:42:14,500 --> 00:42:16,140
Future doctor right there.

604
00:42:16,180 --> 00:42:18,680
With his personality, perfect for the job.

605
00:42:19,220 --> 00:42:20,620
When I need check-ups later,

606
00:42:20,660 --> 00:42:22,160
I'm booking him, no second thoughts.

607
00:42:23,040 --> 00:42:24,580
Enough about illnesses.

608
00:42:24,620 --> 00:42:26,420
Let's focus on the good stuff.

609
00:42:26,460 --> 00:42:29,100
Just imagine us someday
flying together on Yu Qiao's plane.

610
00:42:29,680 --> 00:42:33,020
Northern Aviation University,
that's insanely competitive,

611
00:42:33,060 --> 00:42:34,340
yet he got in like it was nothing.

612
00:42:35,160 --> 00:42:36,540
All our kids

613
00:42:36,580 --> 00:42:37,680
are making us proud.

614
00:42:37,720 --> 00:42:38,560
Exactly!

615
00:42:39,260 --> 00:42:41,440
Hasn't your Fangyuan
already made it as a boss?

616
00:42:41,480 --> 00:42:44,320
Get this. Yesterday,
his dad and I took him shopping

617
00:42:44,360 --> 00:42:46,200
for school supplies, but guess what?

618
00:42:46,740 --> 00:42:47,880
The young man turned the tables

619
00:42:47,920 --> 00:42:49,020
and used his own money

620
00:42:49,060 --> 00:42:51,360
to buy us new outfits instead.

621
00:42:51,400 --> 00:42:52,640
Really?

622
00:42:53,200 --> 00:42:54,240
Nice.

623
00:42:54,940 --> 00:42:56,220
And to think you used to

624
00:42:56,260 --> 00:42:58,980
complain Fangyuan drove you crazy,
remember?

625
00:42:59,020 --> 00:43:00,180
Well, look at him now,

626
00:43:00,920 --> 00:43:02,060
built his own internet empire

627
00:43:02,100 --> 00:43:04,180
with such a big success.

628
00:43:04,680 --> 00:43:05,720
Right!

629
00:43:05,760 --> 00:43:07,240
Your Fangyuan's killing it. What a star!

630
00:43:07,280 --> 00:43:08,120
Exactly.

631
00:43:08,160 --> 00:43:10,760
Sure, he's no natural at studying.

632
00:43:11,260 --> 00:43:13,620
But he got into a decent university
in Shanghai.

633
00:43:14,120 --> 00:43:15,400
That's more than enough for me.

634
00:43:15,440 --> 00:43:16,920
Plus, he got to keep Du Shang as buddies.

635
00:43:18,880 --> 00:43:21,900
At least Yingtao and Yu Qiao
can look out for each other in Hongyang.

636
00:43:22,700 --> 00:43:25,460
But Yunyun? She could've gone too,

637
00:43:25,500 --> 00:43:26,860
yet chose to stay home alone.

638
00:43:27,400 --> 00:43:29,880
That girl's got a good heart.
She just wants to stay close to her dad.

639
00:43:31,600 --> 00:43:33,520
Daughters really are the best,
so thoughtful.

640
00:43:34,020 --> 00:43:34,920
Not like sons.

641
00:43:35,420 --> 00:43:36,820
Our Cai Fangyuan,

642
00:43:36,860 --> 00:43:39,280
even talking in his sleep,
he's begging to go to Shanghai.

643
00:43:40,120 --> 00:43:40,960
Juan,

644
00:43:41,760 --> 00:43:43,700
how's Yingtao been lately?

645
00:43:45,840 --> 00:43:47,380
She seems fine on the surface,

646
00:43:47,880 --> 00:43:50,400
but who knows what's brewing beneath?

647
00:43:51,080 --> 00:43:52,760
Yesterday she insisted on

648
00:43:52,800 --> 00:43:56,220
going to Hongyang alone, wouldn't even
let me or her dad see her off.

649
00:43:56,720 --> 00:43:58,900
Really makes you wonder
what's going on in that head of hers.

650
00:44:00,820 --> 00:44:03,140
This doesn't sound like Yingtao at all.

